Raymond R. Ramu 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Customer Officer at SAIA INC, Raymond R. Ramu  made $725,191 in total compensation.  Of this total $342,610 was received as a salary, $89,851 was received as a bonus, $134,280 was received in stock options, $127,505 was awarded as stock and $30,945 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


